		<div class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar_item">	
			<br>
			<br>
			<p> <b> WELCOME TO AEON LAB! </b> <br> <br>	
            We explore <b> circuits & systems based on nanoscaled CMOS and emerging nanotechnologies for energy-efficient, high performance computing applications</b>. Currently we are focusing in the areas of <b> neuromorphic computing, wearable healthcare devices, and hardware security </b>.  </p>  			
            			
		  </div><!--close sidebar_item--> 
        </div><!--close sidebar-->  
